@steipete | ❤️ 38 | 🔁 1 | 💬 2 | 👁 3735

Two experiments in the next @openclaw to address some &quot;GPT is lazy&quot; issues: 
1) Strict mode:

agents.defaults.embeddedPi.executionContract = &quot;strict-agentic&quot;

This tells GPT-5.x to keep working: read more code, call tools, make changes, or return a real blocker instead of stopping at “here’s the plan.” https://t.co/QMdeus6Y5J

